---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us — Società Filarmonica di Turriaco" lang="en" currentPage="chisiamo">
  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="intro-quote">
        <em>With an uninterrupted activity spanning three centuries of history, the Società Filarmonica di Turriaco is one of the most deeply rooted and tradition-rich brass bands in the entire Friuli Venezia Giulia region.</em>
      </p>

      <p>The first &ldquo;banda di Turriaco&rdquo; was founded in 1870, on the initiative of a small group of local music enthusiasts.</p>

      <p>Its first steps were taken under the direction of maestro Guglielmo Szubert, and it was formally constituted as the <em>Società Filarmonica di Turriaco</em> in December 1900. After various vicissitudes — including an internal split that led, at the turn of the century, to the coexistence of two distinct bands — it found its definitive form in 1920, maintaining it until March 2017 when, by unanimous decision of the members' assembly, it was transformed into a Social Promotion Association (APS).</p>

      <p>A witness to the historical evolution that transformed the Isonzo lands from Habsburg territory to an integral part of the Italian state, the ensemble represents an exceptional <em>trait d'union</em> between the most recent musical trends and the rhythms and sounds of Central European culture.</p>

      <p>The ensemble currently consists of around thirty active members, joined — depending on the occasion — by friends who enjoy making music together with us.</p>

      <p>Independent in its organisational and administrative management, the Association is governed by a board of directors elected by the members' assembly.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <figure class="banda-photo">
        <img
          src={`${base}/asset/images/fotobanda.jpg`}
          alt="Group photo — Società Filarmonica di Turriaco"
        />
        <figcaption>The Turriaco Band at the 2025 Christmas Concert</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Board of Directors -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Board of Directors</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="board-list">
        <li><strong>Andrea Baldo</strong> — President</li>
        <li><strong>Susanna Bertogna</strong> — Vice-President</li>
        <li>Sofia Bazzara</li>
        <li>Marco Cerni</li>
        <li>Danilo Fum</li>
        <li>Eva Moschioni</li>
        <li>Franco Nocent</li>
        <li>Sergio Passon</li>
        <li>Michele Poclen</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Conductor -->
  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container prose">
      <div class="section-header">    
      <h2>The Conductor</h2>
      </div>
      <p>The Società Filarmonica is currently directed by Maestro <strong>Fulvio Dose</strong>, who leads the ensemble with passion and expertise, keeping alive the link with tradition while promoting innovation in the repertoire. (Click on the name to view the CV)</p>
      <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; margin-top: 16px;">
        <div style="text-align: center; width: 160px;">
          <img src={`${base}/asset/images/fotodose.png`} alt="Maestro Fulvio Dose" style="width: 136px; height: 136px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; display: block; margin: 0 auto 10px; border: 2px solid var(--color-secondary);" />
          <a href={`${base}/en/curriculum/dose`} title="Curriculum — Fulvio Dose" style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--color-secondary); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; font-family: var(--font-body);">Fulvio Dose</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

